OL,3,CBoy, 16, in serious condition in
OL,4,Chospital following machete attack
OL,6,FA 16 year-old boy has been seriously
OL,7,Finjured in a machete attack in Dudley.
OL,9,FThe teenager was taken to hospital
OL,10,Fwhere he remains in a serious but
OL,11,Fstable condition.
OL,13,FPolice were called to reports of
OL,14,Fviolence and a group of people with
OL,15,Fmachetes just before 2pm yesterday on
OL,16,FDuncan Edwards Close.
OL,18,FThe victim is believed to have been
OL,19,Fwalking in the area when he was
OL,20,Fapproached by two young men on a moped
OL,21,Fwho attacked him before fleeing.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
