OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1779714673
OL,3,CBoy, 16, in serious condition in
OL,4,Chospital following machete attack
OL,6,FHe was left with serious injuries to
OL,7,Fhis chest and face and has undergone
OL,8,Fsurgery.
OL,10,FPolice have recovered CCTV and mobile
OL,11,Fphone footage and are urging the
OL,12,Fpublic to help them identify those
OL,13,Finvolved, using this dedicated page.
OL,15,FAdditional patrols are taking place in
OL,16,Fthe area today.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
