OL,3,CBoy, 16, in serious condition in
OL,4,Chospital following machete attack
OL,6,FA spokesperson from West Midlands
OL,7,FPolice said: "This was an horrific
OL,8,Fattack in the middle of the day and it
OL,9,Fcould easily have resulted in this boy
OL,10,Flosing his life.
OL,12,F"We've been working tirelessly since
OL,13,Fthen to understand exactly what
OL,14,Fhappened, and who was responsible, and
OL,15,FI'd urge anyone with information to
OL,16,Fget in touch with as soon as possible."
